Inheritance 

Reuse of already defined classes with a is a relationship is known
As inheritance.

Inheritance support concept of reusability.

Inheritance basically applied to classes.


  Polymorphism

Polymorphism means Same message given to generalize things for 
Same behavior but implemented  differently.

Polymorphism allow object to decide that which form of function 
Have to implement at compile time also at runtime.

Polymorphism basically applied to functions or methods.
